      "markdown": "PECIAL RESERVE\n\nAtR\nRCE .N\n\nR.57733\n\n<!-- PageHeader: POSTED TO RCAF Manning Pool, Toronto TRADE Std. Aircrewman -->\n\n\n![oPilo](figures/1.1)\n\n\n# ROYAL CANADIAN AIR FORCE (ATTESTATION PAPER)\n\nAPR 19 1910\n\n(Pages one and two, only, are to be completed in Applicant's own Handwriting)\n\nT-130-A-49\n\n1\\. Surname acland\n\nFULL Christian Names.\nlon Hugh\n\n2\\. Present Address\nPatricia Bay aerodrome\n\nTelephone Sid-155\n11\n\n3\\. Permanent Address.\n.\n.\n\\-\n\n4\\. Place of Birth\nVictoria. B.C.\n\nCitizenship British Subject.\n\n5\\. Date of Birth\n17.10.14\n\nMarried, Single, Widower, Separated, Divorced\nSingle\n\n6\\. Particulars of Children\n4.5.\n\n\n<table>\n<tr>\n<th>.<br>Name</th>\n<th>Date of birth</th>\n<th>Name</th>\n<th>Date of birth</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>.</td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td>+</td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n\n\n7\\. Occupation\nass't. Engineer\n\n8\\. Religion C.of.E.\nState denomination\n\n9\\. Languages.\nEnglish\n\nState proficiency\n\n10\\. Next of Kin (Full Name)\nJohn Bevill Geland\n\nRelationship Father\n\" Address Cowichau Bay. Vartcouver Island. B.C.\n\n11\\. Father (Full Name)\nJohn Bevill Geland\n\nBirthplace.\nEngland\n\n\" Address.\nCowichan Bay. V.I.\n\nCitizenship British Subject\n\n\" Occupation\nHotel manager.\n\n12\\. Mother (Full Maiden Name)\nmarjorie Geland Birthplace.\n\nu.s.a.\n\n\"\nAddress\nCovichan Bay\nCitizenship\nBritish Subject.\n\n13\\. Details of any Naval, Military or Air Force Service:\n\n\n<table>\n<tr>\n<th rowspan=\"2\">Unit</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\">Place</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\">Rank</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\">Trade</th>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Date</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\">Reason for discharge</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th>From</th>\n<th>To</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></td>\n<td></